        "subject": "LU-6418 llite: Simplify code of ll_direct_rw_pages",
        "message": "LU-6418 llite: Simplify code of ll_direct_rw_pages\n\nIn function ll_direct_rw_pages, the cl_page_find will return a\ncl_page with cp_type with value of CPT_TRANSIENT for sure. And\nit will not cache this type of cl_page anymore. This patch remove\nthe code of logical when cp_type is equal to CPT_CACHEABLE which\nis needed in old version.\n\nSigned-off-by: Wu Libin <lwu@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I6634c31dca65a54ad6d0e092554c033403315077\n"
      },
